title: Sensing The Good Things Has In Store | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Sensing The Good Things Has In Store | Joel Osteen
description:
When God laid out the plan for your life, He lined up moments of favor in your future. He's prepared the right breaks and opportunities to get you where you need to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
